Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:03.10,DogDays-narrator,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,The summer vacation I was \Nlooking forward to so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:07.62,DogDays-narrator,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Little did I know, our destination  \Nwas actually another world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.99,DogDays-narrator,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,As for my two childhood friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.58,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:12.82,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.57,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting for duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.49,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.04,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.72,DogDays-ep-title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Pastillage Joins The Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:59.13,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that both armies' \Nheroes are going for each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:02.10,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink is dashing \Nthrough the cog area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:04.56,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,I have about 100 days of \Nexperience being a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.31,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that newbie \Nhero, Nanami, beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:11.27,DogDays-main,Ecl,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, show them your experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.06,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.36,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, do you think you can \Nuphold your teacher's honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:20.70,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I mean I am \NSink's older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.83,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Nanami is jumping into the \Nfray with Her Excellency Leon,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.96,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,but the Biscotti army \Nmoves in to defend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.90,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Sink, I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.28,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.04,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,The hero battle has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.25,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,It's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.18,DogDays-main,leo,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like things are \Nheating up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.26,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,But still, having the hero battle steal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.77,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all of the attention \Nis a bit unsatisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.39,DogDays-main,Ecl,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-sama, may we request a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.81,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I shall take \Nyou both on at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.11,DogDays-main,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.94,DogDays-main,girls,0000,0000,0000,,The items go over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.53,DogDays-main,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.74,DogDays-overlap,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.87,DogDays-main,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,They got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.50,DogDays-main,Jau,0000,0000,0000,,We need clothes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.67,DogDays-main,Godw,0000,0000,0000,,You three! What's with that getup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.46,DogDays-main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,You perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.59,DogDays-main,Vert,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.88,DogDays-main,Godw,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.01,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:01.92,DogDays-main,Godw,0000,0000,0000,,My prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.13,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Godwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.89,DogDays-main,Godw,0000,0000,0000,,How was your fight with the hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.85,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that guy's actually \Ngotten quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.14,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't lying when he said that \Nhe's been training really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.19,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we also have a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.90,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,things are getting quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.02,DogDays-main,Godw,0000,0000,0000,,Quite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.94,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Here in the waterfall area,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.65,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-sama and the Biscotti \NCombo are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.20,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze Ninja Art: Dual Lightning Blossom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:41.76,DogDays-main,Ecl,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.26,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.63,DogDays-main,Ecl,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.85,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:06.70,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,Lion King: Conflagration Explosive Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.96,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That was really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.75,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,I told you: too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.89,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Secret Squad's \Nuniform is made to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.27,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,maximize mobility, \Ngetting hit is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.14,DogDays-main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:40.69,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy, Sink.\N Flonyard-style war is really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.48,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.45,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,I just knew you'd like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.20,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Leon-sama is cute and cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.29,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the Galettians are nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.70,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,The Biscottians are all fun and kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.30,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce them all \Nto you and Becky later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.51,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.22,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.64,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:16.98,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...win this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.82,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune Water Emblem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.65,DogDays-main,SinK,0000,0000,0000,,Infernal Fire Emblem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.11,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.79,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Beams! They just shot beams...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.71,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that would be the Emblem Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.63,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a finishing move of \Nthe knight class fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.34,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.14,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:07:00.06,DogDays-main,Ric,0000,0000,0000,,Our hero's in trouble! \NWe have to aid him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:05.11,DogDays-main,Vert,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Rico-chan's making \Na move! Archers, take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.70,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-sama herself taught \Nme this Emblem Cannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.30,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Both heros' armor have been destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:36.14,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,but like a true hero, the important \Nparts are still covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.93,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, showing you this much is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.64,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,How is that okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.86,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,It's not underwear,\N so it's not embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.32,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Nanami is not set back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:49.82,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it looks like the heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.15,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,need to change their equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.70,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,They are both falling back, for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.49,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it's still the first half;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.16,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.29,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.75,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,Farkas, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:10.84,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake, \Nthis girl's definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.84,location,Txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}First Half of the Battle - Lunch Break\NFournette Terrace
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.39,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, do you know how shocked I was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.97,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,You could have at least explained \Nsome of it beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.98,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I already said "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.64,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, Becky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.10,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.19,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things you love, like sightseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.73,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and trying different foods, are also in the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.36,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,I've also thought of a bunch of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.66,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,You should come to Galette, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.74,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to a bunch \Nof tasty fish dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.58,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Leon-sama, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.75,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.71,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you should also try joining the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.29,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wanted you to join, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.88,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.09,DogDays-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Boo, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.38,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Don't both of you make \Nthe same face at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.01,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying myself\N enough just watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.31,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.77,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to enjoy my nice conversation \Nwith the princess more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.77,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.94,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy our girl talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.28,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.45,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Leo-nee, Millihi-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.24,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.33,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,Couvertete? Callaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.00,DogDays-main,MilL,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:31.25,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to- Pastillage wants \Nto join this battle, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.92,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we've come \Nto collect that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.85,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.42,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the lunch break is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.34,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,the afternoon activities can begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.55,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Both armies have ordered their formations
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.74,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and are perfectly prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:10:00.22,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Our analysts are joining \Nthe afternoon battle as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.72,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-sama and Princess Millihi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.81,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,have taken their command posts \Nin their respective HQs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:09.21,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,The princess looks so dignified in her battle clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.10,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The afternoon's deciding \Nbattle is about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.80,DogDays-main,COU,0000,0000,0000,,Put that war on hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.19,DogDays-main,COU,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, the First Princess of \Nthe Principality of Pastillage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.30,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Couverte Eschenbach Pastillage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.06,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Couverte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.60,DogDays-main,Rico,0000,0000,0000,,Cou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.27,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,Cou-sama, what's the occasion today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:36.61,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,You know exactly what's up, Millihi-nee! \NAnd you, too, Leo-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.86,DogDays-main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:44.08,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,I know war games aren't \Nthat popular in our land,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.62,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not fair that only you get
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.12,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to summon heroes and have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.29,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy if you wanted to join,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.00,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but what should we do about \Nrules and winning conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.13,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,About that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.97,DogDays-main,MilL,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.14,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,My target is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:10.69,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take our guest from\Nthe other world as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.57,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with her on first sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.12,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to seduce her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.33,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,If you want her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.04,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to defeat \NPastillage's pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.17,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the 40 airborne knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:34.88,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:40.01,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,...and 150 Eschenbach High Speed Cavalry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.63,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,before you can get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:48.10,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,For Galette, it doesn't really \Nmatter where Rebecca resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:52.02,DogDays-main,Leon,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan is to simply defeat \Nboth Pastillage and Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.44,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder what our hero will decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.77,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,I personally want to \Nget Rebecca-san back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.69,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.86,DogDays-main,Brio,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that was her plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.16,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.08,DogDays-main,Gau,0000,0000,0000,,So you heroes have to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.24,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.91,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes, what do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.08,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'll accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.67,DogDays-narrator,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.17,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Then would the representatives \Nof the three countries
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.47,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,please signal the beginning of battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.89,DogDays-main,Cou,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.55,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,battle royale between all three countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:30.39,DogDays-main,Mill,0000,0000,0000,,An all out battle for \Ngetting the top score!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.81,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The two heroes will rescue Rebecca-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:38.86,DogDays-main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle of Fournette Lake, \NAfternoon Match, begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.28,DogDays-main,rol,0000,0000,0000,,So you were able to enter \Nthe fray, Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:48.14,DogDays-main,ber,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to pin Rolan down. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.95,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,The Leader of the Knights, Rolan, \Nis already heading for the lake area!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:55.16,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,General Bernard is also rushing ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.55,DogDays-main,COU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to \Ndelay the heroes, Callaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.80,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.85,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,Liscia, can you handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.81,DogDays-main,Lisc,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Callaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.77,DogDays-main,Lisc,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, load your rifles with Emblem Rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.89,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.31,DogDays-main,Lisc,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.45,DogDays-main,Rol,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage's airborne mage\Nsquad is a real bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.99,DogDays-main,Ban,0000,0000,0000,,If they are left unchecked, \Nour formations will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.66,DogDays-main,Lisc,0000,0000,0000,,I've spotted both armies' captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.41,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Initiate focus fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.08,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.42,DogDays-main,Ban,0000,0000,0000,,Rolan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.96,DogDays-main,Rol,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Bernard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.75,DogDays-main,Rol,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.51,DogDays-main,Lisc,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man, it's so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.80,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,They are unscathed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.89,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,That was Iron Defense Rolan's \Nfamous protective Emblem Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:55.93,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.44,DogDays-main,Bern,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.61,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,General Bernard's long distance Emblem Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.86,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It's super effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.82,DogDays-main,Lisc,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.29,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,The two captains put up a united front!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.21,DogDays-main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Create a path for our armies by cleaving
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.92,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,into the front lines of the mage-knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.79,DogDays-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.17,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,On this side, the Biscotti and \NGalette knights are working
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.17,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,together from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.43,DogDays-main,Vert,0000,0000,0000,,Rico-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.72,DogDays-main,rico,0000,0000,0000,,Vert-nee, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.77,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,But Pastillage's mages aren't sitting idle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.39,DogDays-main,wom,0000,0000,0000,,Precision Marksman Squad! Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.94,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage is the technology leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.65,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Their magical research is \Nthe best on the continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.49,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage's unique crystal magic \Nshines on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:00.83,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Our fight's on hold, \Nlet's go rescue Becky together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.08,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.67,DogDays-main,calla,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, honored heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:11.88,DogDays-main,calla,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca-sama is a valued guest \Nof my master, Couverte-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:14.68,DogDays-main,calla,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, they are having \Nan important conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.06,DogDays-main,calla,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that I can't let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:25.06,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Pastillage's unique Sky Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.32,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,ride on giant birds named Blanchir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:30.61,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,How are the heroes going to \Nfight against the Sky Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.45,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,Emblem Sword Skill: Spinner Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.87,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:45.00,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,Arc Sign, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.00,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:51.97,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.84,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, can you use Bright Power Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.85,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.93,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Then watch and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.14,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Materialize the emblem and \Ngather your Bright Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:05.52,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Then try to visualize the shape of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.86,DogDays-main,Sink,0000,0000,0000,,Tornader! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.99,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.03,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink's Bright Power Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.58,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The airboard Tornader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.62,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.59,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Bright Power... focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.09,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.30,DogDays-narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Nanami, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.93,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.02,DogDays-main,Ann2,0000,0000,0000,,She summoned her Bright Power Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.19,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.36,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,Galette's the capital of water, \Nblessed by both ocean and river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.44,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.29,DogDays-main,nana,0000,0000,0000,,am going to be the surfer hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.79,DogDays-narrator,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Nanami is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.13,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.22,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please return Becky to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.60,DogDays-main,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.10,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,You really are heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.68,DogDays-main,Cara,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.85,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's something happening in \Nthe central battlefield as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:32.32,DogDays-main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I thought I'd be fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.82,DogDays-main,Brio,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, fighting together \Nis quite nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.91,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,The "Peerless" and the \N"Strongest on the continent!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:43.70,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest of Biscotti and \NGalette formed the ultimate team!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.75,DogDays-main,vio,0000,0000,0000,,They both seem to enjoy themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.08,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so should we just follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.63,DogDays-main,yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.21,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the leaders of the Imperial Guard and \Nthe Secret Squad are with them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.47,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Does this spell certain \Ndoom for Pastillage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:01.35,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected, our \Ntroops are in a real bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.47,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:06.23,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,I think we have no choice but \Nfor you to go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.02,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,B-but you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.40,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,as I said before, I really can't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:13.86,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,fight like Sink or Nanami, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.20,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said you have to fight like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.33,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Rebecca, when I saw \Nyou for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.62,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my senses tingled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.12,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,You have the same eyes as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.66,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:31.21,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,You aspire to be like your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.13,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,"If only I could do that, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.17,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we could spend more time together."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.63,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:40.59,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,I aspire to be like \NMillihi-nee and Leo-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:44.10,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a wonderful ruler \Nloved by my subjects, like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.23,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,But, your athletic skills \Nare on the sad side,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.14,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm useless in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.61,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,However, in Pastillage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.90,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we have something that allows \Neven us to do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.70,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Our crystal magic, and \NPastillage's Treasure Swords:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.66,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Spear Culmurth and \NDivine Sword Mercurius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.04,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,These are the perfect swords \Nfor us mages types.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.96,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mage type?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:16.71,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm actually still training \Nto be the next ruler of my land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.51,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I've been \Nentrusted with the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.38,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.68,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,That might not sound encouraging,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.56,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like we can understand \Neach other better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.52,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try a bunch of firsts with you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.89,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,since I feel like we'll really get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:35.73,DogDays-main,reb,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored, but are you \Nsure you really want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.40,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.65,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.66,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,I want take the skies with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.41,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.70,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,will you accept Pastillage's \NDivine Sword Mercurius?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.71,DogDays-narrator,ann,0000,0000,0000,,Something's happening on the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.92,DogDays-narrator,ann2,0000,0000,0000,,...flying terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.76,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.76,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,And Heroes from Galette and Biscotti:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.76,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,too bad, but you're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:14.19,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Our army's secret weapon has just been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.77,DogDays-main,cou,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.15,DogDays-main,Reb,0000,0000,0000,,Equip!
